description: Manage Azure API Management API Version Set.

commands.name: az apim api versionset create
examples: az apim api versionset create --resource-group MyResourceGroup --service-name MyServiceName --version-set-id MyVersionSetId --display-name MyDisplayName --versioning-scheme "Header" --description MyDescription --version-header-name MyHeaderName

az apim api versionset create --resource-group MyResourceGroup --service-name MyServiceName --version-set-id MyVersionSetId --display-name MyDisplayName --versioning-scheme "Query" --description MyDescription --version-query-name MyQueryName

commands.name: az apim api versionset delete
examples: az apim api versionset delete --resource-group MyResourceGroup --service-name MyServiceName --version-set-id MyVersionSetId

commands.name: az apim api versionset list
commands.summary: Lists a collection of API Version Sets in the specified service instance.
examples: az apim api versionset list --resource-group MyResourceGroup --service-name MyServiceName

commands.name: az apim api versionset show
commands.summary: Gets the details of the Api Version Set specified by its identifier.
examples: az apim api versionset show --resource-group MyResourceGroup --service-name MyServiceName --version-set-id MyVersionSetId

commands.name: az apim api versionset update
commands.summary: Updates the details of the Api VersionSet specified by its identifier.
examples: az apim api versionset update --resource-group MyResourceGroup --service-name MyServiceName --version-set-id MyVersionSetId --display-name MyNewDisplayName --description MyNewDescription
az apim api versionset update --resource-group MyResourceGroup --service-name MyServiceName --version-set-id MyVersionSetId --versioning-scheme "Query" --version-query-name MyNewQueryName
